abstract: Our Community continues intensely excited. The cannon taken from the Germans yesterday by the Americans was quietly conveyed from the public landing this afternoon by the former. abstract: The excitement in this city is on the increase. The Germans refused to give up the cannon, consequently fighting has commenced over the Canal, and it is reported several have been killed. abstract: RIVERHEAD, Suffolk Co., Wednesday, April 4, 1855. The Know-Nothings nominated their ticket in this town and thought they should elect it. abstract: The intelligence Itom Erurope is interesting, without being of over an average importance. The Congress of Vienna held four conferences, in respect to which the strictest secrecy is observed. Light is not compatible with the proceeding of diplomacy. abstract: The Government of Brazil seems to have definitely determined that the great Amazon River shall not be opened to foreign navigation. If this decision is maintained, the immense valleys drained by this mighty stream and its numerous tributaries, and possessing elements of prosperity and wealth rarely excelled, must continue to be withheld from the uses and deprived of the benefits of commerce, and the arts of thorough civilization which follow commerce in its every track.

abstract: The steamer Prometheus has arrived, with dates from San Francisco to the 24th March. Business of every description is reported as being extremely dull. abstract: BROADWAY THEATRE.-Of the three Roman plays written by SHAKSPEARE, "Coriolanus" deals mostly with the masses, and from it we learn that the immortal bard was no tolerator of bread riots. The voxpopuli was not the vox dei in his estimation, but something of a less healthful and more offensive nature. The sovereign people, as depicted in this tragedy, is a vacillating, cowardly, time-serving crowd, good humored enough, but contemptible, in spite of joviality.

abstract: To the Editor of the New--York Daily Times: I have just received dispatches from Independence. The mail from Utah arrived here yesterday.
